      "parameters": {
        "content": "# 🌙 Daily Inbox Summary\n\nRuns every day at **12:05 AM**.\n\nBuilds an AI-powered summary of the previous day's inbox from the email logs stored in Google Sheets. The report includes inbox statistics, upcoming events, reply drafts, and spam cleanup, then delivers a single MailWise digest email.\n",
