        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Below are all emails processed today.\nGenerate a professional daily inbox report.\n\nStart with a quick overview including:\n• Total emails processed\n• Number of urgent emails\n• Opportunities\n• College/TnP\n• Bills\n• Informational\n• Spam\n\nThen include:\n\n## Upcoming Events\nMention today's detected events.\n\n## Reply Drafts\nMention emails where replyNeeded was true.\n\n## Spam Cleaned Today\n\nMention all spam emails that were automatically moved to Trash.\n\nFor each include:\n- Subject\n- Sender\n- One-line summary\n\nMention that Gmail Trash retains emails for 30 days if the user wants to restore one.\n\n## Important Emails\nProvide concise bullet points.\n\n## Action Items\nList anything the user should do tomorrow.\n\nKeep the report concise and easy to scan.\n\nUse the events list when writing the Upcoming Events section.\n\nUse the replyEmails list when writing the Reply Drafts section.\nUpcoming Events:\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.events, null, 2) }}\n\nReply Drafts Required:\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.replyEmails, null, 2) }}\n\nStatistics:\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.stats, null, 2) }}\n\nToday's processed emails (one email per section):\n\n{{ $json.emails }}\n\nSpam Emails:\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.spamEmails, null, 2) }}",
        "batching": {}
